		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<div><p>Собственно вот тестовое задание авторства Дмитрия Васина для данной вакансии, это задание выдается кандидату без собеседования:</p>

<p>You are asked to&nbsp;analyze and design a&nbsp;better solution for the fare service in&nbsp;the Kyiv subway.<br>• Please propose a&nbsp;plan on&nbsp;how you’ll approach to&nbsp;design the new service. Describe the goals and the expected results for each stage.<br>• Describe major gaps for improvement and key user scenarios.<br>• Create the detailed interaction design for the proposed solution (could be&nbsp;self-service kiosk or&nbsp;any other option).</p>

<p>Think big, but make things easy and straightforward, and please don’t feel constrained.</p></div>
		</div>

