			<p>Sorry for troubling you i&nbsp;would like to&nbsp;know, if&nbsp;this company has some training for students in&nbsp;Lviv? Thanks...</p>
		</div>

				<a class="review-link" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/epam-systems/reviews/25107/">
					Ссылка
				</a>

			<div class="sup-users">
					<span></span>
			</div>

	</div>
</div>

    
