				<span class="prof">
						Founder в <span>Jet SnaiL, LLC</span>
				</span>


				<a class="comment-link" href="#18908">23 января 2009 18:06</a>
			</div>

		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<p>To&nbsp;eghik_v_tumane:<br>Ukrainskiy ya&nbsp;ne&nbsp;znayu, ya&nbsp;viros v&nbsp;Odesse. Russkiy&nbsp;— prosto ne&nbsp;hotel pisat’ translitom. Vmesto togo 4tobi plakat’ na&nbsp;forume v&nbsp;rabo4ee vremya&nbsp;— rabotaite ili ishite rabotu. Mne nravitsa mentalitet ukraincev&nbsp;— kto-to i&nbsp;4to-to za&nbsp;vas doljen delat’, a&nbsp;vi&nbsp;sidite i&nbsp;jdete. Kak govoritsa&nbsp;— “Yojiki plakali, kololis’ no&nbsp;prodoljali est’ kaktus”.</p>
		</div>

				<a class="review-link" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/epam-systems/reviews/18908/">
