				<span class="prof">
						Founder в <span>Jet SnaiL, LLC</span>
				</span>


				<a class="comment-link" href="#18906">23 января 2009 17:51</a>
			</div>

		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<p>I&nbsp;left EPAM Systems in&nbsp;September 2008, just before so&nbsp;called “crisis”, and&nbsp;I feel very happy about that! From my&nbsp;point of&nbsp;view, there is&nbsp;no&nbsp;crisis in&nbsp;IT industry. I&nbsp;keep getting so&nbsp;many offers so&nbsp;I can’t even reply to&nbsp;all of&nbsp;them. Yeah, todays situation on&nbsp;the market is&nbsp;overall worse and weak companies (or&nbsp;departments) keep losing projects and can’t feed all developers they were feeding yesterday. It&nbsp;is&nbsp;OK, guys, you had to&nbsp;be&nbsp;prepared for that. I&nbsp;see it&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;motivation to&nbsp;find other better jobs for those who really deserve&nbsp;it. You’ve got to&nbsp;understand that companies don’t owe you anything unless specified by&nbsp;contract. Screaming here won’t help you keep your bills paid. So&nbsp;suck it&nbsp;up, update your resume and shop for a&nbsp;better job. Good luck!</p>
		</div>

				<a class="review-link" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/epam-systems/reviews/18906/">
