				</span>


				<a class="comment-link" href="#16920">17 июня 2008 15:59</a>
			</div>

		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<div><p>здесь спрашивали про курсы...</p>

<p>From August a&nbsp;new Training. NET Course starts at&nbsp;EPAM Training Center. </p>

<p>Training is&nbsp;planned for 1&nbsp;month. Classes start at&nbsp;9&nbsp;a.m. and finish 6&nbsp;p.m. Training is&nbsp;free of&nbsp;charge for all participants.</p>

<p>After the graduation of&nbsp;the training all students will take&nbsp;BB testing and technical interview. Those who will pass test and interview successfully will have chance to&nbsp;work for EPAM starting from Junior Software Engineering positions. </p>

<p>If&nbsp;you have any questions don’t hesitate to&nbsp;ask&nbsp;me.</p></div>
		</div>

				<a class="review-link" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/epam-systems/reviews/16920/">
					Ссылка
				</a>

			<div class="sup-users">
					<span></span>
			</div>

